close_reason: Todos import now preserves canonical optional metadata and the full sequential regression sweep is green.
body: "Current todos export writes full front matter but todos import only hydrates a subset of ItemFrontMatter. This silently drops definition_of_ready, planning metadata, blocked metadata, reviewer/risk/confidence/release, and issue-specific fields on re-import. Update docs first then implement import normalization and regression coverage so round-trips are lossless for canonical fields."
